<branch_naming_rules>
- All new branches MUST start with the `duo/` prefix
- Format: duo/<type>/<identifier>-<short-description>
- Each segment (type, identifier, short-description) must use only lowercase letters, numbers, and hyphens
- No consecutive hyphens (--) or trailing hyphens in any segment
- Types: fix, feature, update, refactor, docs
- Examples: duo/feature/123-user-auth, duo/fix/456-login-bug
</branch_naming_rules>
